<It_G>Can be converted to talent points by dragging it into the orb in the top left of the talent tab of the character window.</It_G>^

column4:

t_korean: making it much stronger than a normal sealed familiar but more fragile.

t_key: <It_G>Can be attached to equipment to boost attributes or add additional effects.</It_G>
<It_G>Alt + Right-click on any piece of equipment with a slot to bring up the sealed familiar attachment window.</It_G>
<It_G>Can be converted to talent points by dragging it into the orb in the top left of the talent tab of the character window.</It_G>
<R_Y>Cannot be extracted. Soul crystal is destroyed when removed.</R_Y>

t_key: <It_G>Can be attached to equipment to boost attributes or add additional effects.</It_G>
<It_G>Alt + Right-click on any piece of equipment with a slot to bring up the sealed familiar attachment window.</It_G>
<It_G>Can be converted to talent points by dragging it into the orb in the top left of the talent tab of the character window.</It_G>^

t_key: ^SF2_CA_00_0002_description^
This crystal contains the soul of a familiar
t_korean: making it much stronger than a normal sealed familiar but more fragile.

t_key: <It_G>Can be attached to equipment to boost attributes or add additional effects.</It_G>
<It_G>Alt + Right-click on any piece of equipment with a slot to bring up the sealed familiar attachment window.</It_G>
<It_G>Can be converted to talent points by dragging it into the orb in the top left of the talent tab of the character window.</It_G>
<R_Y>Cannot be extracted. Soul crystal is destroyed when removed.</R_Y>

t_korean:
making it much stronger than a normal sealed familiar but more fragile.
Can be used to temper familiars.
Can be converted to talent points by dragging it into the orb in the top left of the talent tab of the character window.
Cannot be extracted. Soul crystal is destroyed when removed.

^SF2_101_3_0085_description^
t_korean: ^This seal contains the essence of a familiar.

t_key: <It_G>Can be attached to equipment to boost attributes or add additional effects.</It_G>

^SF2_101_3_0087_description^

This seal contains the essence of a familiar. Can be attached to equipment to boost attributes or add additional effects.

Alt + Right-click on any piece of equipment with a slot to bring up the sealed familiar attachment window.

Can be converted to talent points by dragging it into the orb in the top left of the talent tab of the character window.
